The authors of this dataset refer to the sources of images in this dataset as follows. 
The file names of images in this dataset remain original when downloaded from its original source.
The dataset is collected by selecting images from the following sources:
- Kaggle dataset (https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/kutaykutlu/forest-fire)
- iStock Images (https://www.istockphoto.com/)
- Flicker (https://www.flickr.com/)
- Google Images (https://www.google.com/search?q=aerial+satellite+first+wildfire+images).
